import React from 'react'
import {FormContainer, FormBody, FormLogBox, FormForm, FormInputPass } from './SignupElements'


const SignUp = () => {
    return (
        <FormBody>
            <FormContainer>
               <FormLogBox>
                <FormForm>
                    <FormInputPass />
                </FormForm>
               </FormLogBox>
            </FormContainer>
        </FormBody>
    )
}

export default SignUp
